@{
    ViewBag.Title = "About";
}

<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
    <meta charset="utf-8" />
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0" />
    <style>
        body {
            background-color: #F8F9FA;
        }
        main {
            text-align: center;
        }

        h2 {
            font-size: 3.5em;
            font-family: "Trebuchet MS";
            margin-bottom: 12px;
            font-weight: bold;
            margin-top: 2%;
            margin-bottom: 1%;
        }

        .founder-story {
            margin: 0 auto;
            text-align: left;
            max-width: 1100px;
        }

        .founder-story p {
            margin-bottom: 20px;
            font-family: 'Times New Roman', serif;
            font-size: 1.3em;
        }

        .image-gallery {
            display: flex;
            justify-content: center;
            align-items: center;
            flex-wrap: wrap;
            gap: 30px; /* Adjust the gap between images */
        }

        .image-gallery img {
            width: 410px; /* Adjust the image width as needed */
            height: 370px; /* Adjust the image height as needed */
            object-fit: cover;
            border-radius: 8px; /* Add border-radius for rounded corners */
            transition: transform 0.3s ease-in-out;
            /*filter: grayscale(70%);*/
        }

        .image-gallery img:hover {
            transform: scale(1.1); /* Add a simple scaling effect on hover */
        }
        .container.body-content {
            margin-top: 0; /* Remove the default top margin */
            margin-bottom: 0;
        }
        .cards-container {
            display: flex;
            justify-content: space-around;
            align-items: flex-start;
            flex-wrap: wrap;
            gap: 30px;
            margin-top: 30px;
        }

        .card {
            max-width: 30%;
            height: 70%;
            border: 1px solid #ddd;
            border-radius: 8px;
            overflow: hidden;
        }

            .card img {
                width: 100%;
                height: 40vh;
                object-fit: cover;
            }

        .card-content {
            padding: 15px;
        }

            .card-content h3 {
                font-size: 1.5em;
                margin-bottom: 10px;
            }

            .card-content p {
                font-size: 1.1em;
                color: #555;
            }
        .card:hover {
            transform: scale(1.05);
        }
    </style>

</head>
<body>
    <main aria-labelledby="title">
        <h2 id="title">Founder Story</h2>
        <div class="founder-story">
            <p>
                At Thriftify, the roots of our business are deeply intertwined with a shared passion for sustainable living and the belief that every used item has a story to tell. Founded by Tamara Stojanova, our journey began in 2024 with a mission to create a marketplace that celebrates the beauty of pre-loved items. Tamara embarked on this venture inspired by the desire to offer a platform where individuals could buy and sell a diverse array of used things, fostering a sense of community and environmental responsibility.
            </p>
        </div>

        <div class="cards-container">
            <div class="card">
                <img src="https://amelieclements.com/wp-content/uploads/2022/02/business-portrait-woman-photographer-zurich-professional-headshot-amelie-clements-corporate-photoshoot-portfolio-apercu.jpg" alt="Image 1">
                <div class="card-content">
                    <h3>Sophia Reynolds</h3>
                    <p>Sophia Reynolds leads Tech Innovate Solutions, a tech company renowned for AI solutions.</p>
                </div>
            </div>

            <div class="card">
                <img src="https://img.freepik.com/premium-photo/headshot-close-up-portrait-indian-latin-confident-mature-good-looking-middle-age-leader-ceo-male-businessman-blur-office-background-handsome-hispanic-senior-business-man-smiling-camera_728202-3525.jpg" alt="Image 2">
                <div class="card-content">
                    <h3>Vincent Rodriguez</h3>
                    <p>Alexandra Chen is a sustainability champion, heading EcoSolutions to prominence in green technology.</p>
                </div>
            </div>

            <div class="card">
                <img src="https://mortonvisuals.com/wp-content/gallery/business-portraits-and-headshots-2/cache/Grace-branding-headshot.jpg-nggid03364-ngg0dyn-1637x2048x100-00f0w010c010r110f110r010t010.jpg" alt="Image 3">
                <div class="card-content">
                    <h3>Alexandra Chen</h3>
                    <p>Vincent Rodriguez, a finance expert, guides clients as the Managing Partner at Rodriguez Capital Management.</p>
                </div>
            </div>
        </div>

    </main>
</body>
</html>

